                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12435281" author="hossman" created="Sun, 17 Sep 2006 04:26:25 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;solving this with javascript on the admin page seems like a fine idea .. but i wouldn&apos;t want to try and put redirect logic or &quot;pretty&quot; error messages into the request handlers &amp;#8211; the expectation is that other code will be hitting the /select urls, the query form on the admin interface is just for convinience.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if any javascript guru&apos;s out there would care to whip up a handy function that works well on the major browsers, i&apos;ll happily commit it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12435356" author="tna" created="Mon, 18 Sep 2006 00:05:37 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This should do the trick:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;form name=f1 method=post&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	Query text: &amp;lt;input type=text name=n&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;input type=button value=&apos;GO&apos; onclick=&quot;if(f1.n.value.length==0) alert(&apos;no empty queries, please&apos;); else f1.submit();&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/form&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12435574" author="billa" created="Mon, 18 Sep 2006 21:59:44 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;That works for both firefox and IE7.  Thanks for the code.  I will fix both the admin main page and the &quot;full interface&quot; page.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12435575" author="billa" created="Mon, 18 Sep 2006 22:08:07 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;patch with fix to solr-48&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12435620" author="billa" created="Tue, 19 Sep 2006 02:25:06 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;FYI, the javascript works for safari too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12435726" author="tna" created="Tue, 19 Sep 2006 09:37:39 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Glad to hear all the good news. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12435770" author="billa" created="Tue, 19 Sep 2006 13:34:36 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch commited.  Thanks for the code.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
